# VibeCraft — Epic Fantasy Knight Fighter
#
# High-detail knight with smooth 12-sided cross-sections.
# 773 vertices, 1436 triangles, 10 normals, 9 UVs
#
# Dimensions  : ~2.0 units tall (with raised sword ~3.2)
# Poly count  : 1436 triangles
# Convention  : Y-up, right-handed coordinate system
#
# Features:
#   - Smooth rounded helm with golden crest
#   - Full plate armor with 12-sided cross-sections
#   - Dramatic pauldrons with gold trim
#   - Flowing crimson cape with wave detail
#   - Kite shield with boss on left arm
#   - Greatsword raised in right hand
#   - Contrapposto stance (alive, dynamic)
#
# Material groups:
#   - armor  (polished steel plate)
#   - gold   (ornamental trim and accents)
#   - cape   (deep crimson fabric)
#   - leather (straps, grip, visor)
#   - blade  (sword steel)
#   - shield (heraldic face)

mtllib fighter.mtl

